Package com.charliai.activities.api

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.charliai.activities.api.Entity
  • public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    The Entity class supports the processing and creation of single entity objects. These can be aggregated in the Entities class.

    kevincollins
